$Id$

2008.07.18 JoungKyun.Kim <http://oops.org> 5.1.0
- fixed make wrong rule on *_HOSTPERPORT
- support iprange on HOSTPER direction and icmp direction
	enable on ALLOWALL *_*_HOSTPERPORT *_ICMP_HOSTPERPING *_ICMP_HOSTPERTRACEROUTE
	syntax:
		10.0.0.1-24        => 10.0.0.1-10.0.0.24
		10.0.0.1-1.24      => 10.0.0.1-10.0.1.24
		10.0.0.1-1.1.24    => 10.0.0.1-10.1.1.24
		10.0.0.1-11.1.1.24 => 10.0.0.1-11.1.1.24
- support no ansi mode print out with -n option

